## About ##

notify-sharp is a C# [D-Bus][] client library for desktop notifications as defined
by the [Desktop Notifications Specification][notification-spec].

## Download ##

 * Source tarball: [notify-sharp-3.0.0.tar.gz][]
 * Git repository on github: [meebey/notify-sharp][github]

 [notify-sharp-3.0.0.tar.gz]: /projects/notify-sharp/downloads/notify-sharp-3.0.0.tar.gz

## Projects using notify-sharp ##

 * [Smuxi IRC Client][Smuxi]
 * [Banshee][]
 * [SparkleShare][]
 * [Tasque][]
 * [Docky][]
 * [GNOME Do][]

